Anubis/Hades/Koga Shuko/Unitron:

::Anubis sighs as lasers pass by his legs and shins, pointing his rifle 
backwards, he fires off a few plasma blasts::
------------------
::Hades yells, firing off a few laser blasts behind him::
------------------
Koga Shuko, turned, firing a missile off at the source of the lasers, a 
grazing his left leg, though the Predacon continued to move.  "Kill him!  
He's ours!" Shuko yelled, pulling out his laser rifle and opening fire on 
Zergling, though it was hard to aim through the foilage.
------------------
Unitron turned around, taking out his other rifle, firing three shots from 
the rifles, charging at Zergling, firing two optic blasts.
